    "desc": "During your Main Phase: You can destroy 1 DARK monster in your hand or face-up field, and if you do, add 1 \"Yubel\", or 1 card that mentions it, from your Deck to your hand, except \"Nightmare Pain\". You can only use this effect of \"Nightmare Pain\" once per turn. While you control a \"Yubel\" monster, your opponent's monsters that can attack must attack \"Yubel\" monsters. Your opponent takes any battle damage you would have taken from battles involving your \"Yubel\" monsters.",
